Privacy Policy for AI Note Assistant

Last updated: [تاريخ اليوم]

1. Introduction
AI Note Assistant ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use our Chrome extension.

2. Information We Collect
Our extension collects and stores the following information locally on your device:
- Notes you create while watching videos
- Video timestamps associated with your notes
- Vocabulary lists you create
- Learning statistics and progress data
- Extension settings and preferences

We do not collect or transmit any personal information to our servers or third parties.

3. How We Use Information
The information collected is used solely to provide the note-taking and learning assistance features of our extension. This includes:
- Displaying your notes and vocabulary lists
- Generating learning statistics
- Personalizing your extension experience based on your settings

4. Data Storage and Security
All data is stored locally on your device using Chrome's storage API. We do not have access to this data, and it is not transmitted over the internet.

5. Third-Party Access
We do not share any user data with third parties. All processing occurs locally within the extension.

6. Your Rights
You can view, edit, or delete your data at any time within the extension settings. Uninstalling the extension will remove all stored data.

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
